{"tid":422866,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖] 見過印象深刻既ux design 係點？","createTime":"2017-10-03T12:15:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-05T06:40:21.000Z","uid":15823,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9f17d1184030aae44f66a2d236f7dbd893668a8c","tid":422866,"uid":15823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T12:15:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/03/201312_bd95fe24ec21156876ce11d7fe9fe090.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F03%2F201312_bd95fe24ec21156876ce11d7fe9fe090.jpg&h=ac8c7cfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今時今日無論app , 網站以至到現實生活裡面既所有野，除左個樣之外，好唔好用都變成左好重要既一環。唔知大家有無見過d 咩印象深刻既ux design 呢？無論眼前一亮定眼前一黑既design 都可以分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11ae8e05a67caf63267d3ef85c038ab791d95f65","tid":422866,"uid":15823,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T12:18:10.000Z","msg":"開始掉磚先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/03/201652_048e158896d1b88c83afc6dc84d4d3a2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F03%2F201652_048e158896d1b88c83afc6dc84d4d3a2.jpg&h=1c08f291&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多時用電話既人都未必好知自己而家做緊咩。如果突然彈個popup 出黎就有機會令人混亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果問之前有一段說明，等佢知道下一步會發生咩事用落就得心應手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f47415d61dcc5268ce1df552bc408d7798ae990e","tid":422866,"uid":15823,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T12:19:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/03/201901_a1c8bd47d617c486f5fb74cf40d29ac0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F03%2F201901_a1c8bd47d617c486f5fb74cf40d29ac0.jpg&h=2d21ff4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家手機上好多時d app 都會問你拎permission , 無論無心又好有意又好，user 都有機會deny 個request<br />\n當去返要用permission 果頁識show 返一個教學點去grant 返permission 俾隻app 就唔會入左黑洞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eb28984dd72c253cb1e2da38b0c0abe26737547","tid":422866,"uid":15823,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T12:21:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/03/202051_1e5a67eb46eeb849761f57ba5253f09b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F03%2F202051_1e5a67eb46eeb849761f57ba5253f09b.jpg&h=ae0586fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時諗design 好多時都會諗個個版面有野個design 係點係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係實際user 用落時經常都會由零開始，所以無野既版面都好重要，加一d 指示或圖案都會幫到user 去了解呢一版點運作"},{"pid":"bf7fc65245937c0bcbcbc0b488a38651db76c435","tid":422866,"uid":15823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T12:50:04.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b991c0d6e052b587affb25ff5503cf70eddfda20","tid":422866,"uid":15823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T13:18:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/03/211202_3f71a46b01dbd6427c362a7fa5b0bc97.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F03%2F211202_3f71a46b01dbd6427c362a7fa5b0bc97.png&h=c7bd88bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本地反面代表: hkdnr<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n右上個hamburger menu 彈出黎連login 都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一堆唔知想點既link，大佬你個網係主要用黎俾人管理個domain 架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最重要果樣野收到咁埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搵左成分鐘先搵到原來login form 係係首頁拉到落最底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nlogin 完個layout 又核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> hea 左少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b296fee39268819418e90458685ff51164fcfb4f","tid":422866,"uid":124445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T13:18:49.000Z","msg":"霎時間諗唔到深刻ux，正所謂好既設計係留意唔到(因為你會用得好順暢)，壞既設計就好突兀易見。<br />\n呢個登既app UX都幾差"},{"pid":"ca9c04aea1b6feb642ffa75e1c34de7db6cf14d7","tid":422866,"uid":40684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T13:22:08.000Z","msg":"整到個UI愈簡單<br />\n會唔會愈user friendly?"},{"pid":"a7d4326a7b5289db9e9e21c319cb8f108c097625","tid":422866,"uid":39065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T13:26:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>整到個UI愈簡單<br />\n會唔會愈user friendly?</blockquote><br />\n我覺得係精簡會貼切D<br />\n<br />\n正如樓主咁講,如果乜都無咁點知下一步點做"},{"pid":"764317daef41a6fbd3e03bded8fd6d7f5924c40d","tid":422866,"uid":15823,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T13:26:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>霎時間諗唔到深刻ux，正所謂好既設計係留意唔到(因為你會用得好順暢)，壞既設計就好突兀易見。<br />\n呢個登既app UX都幾差</blockquote><br />\n講得無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都係去特登留意先cap 底呢d 圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n或者可以分享下唔掂既ux<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 相信每個人都有用一樣野用到想講粗口既一刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例如edo 餅個包裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e763097dfa290f4735866230aa24cc8284f4e00","tid":422866,"uid":15823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T13:28:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>整到個UI愈簡單<br />\n會唔會愈user friendly?</blockquote><br />\n愈簡單當然愈好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但簡單得黎仲可以講到俾user 知佢地要點做就係好難既事<img s